  2,35,"Min mbii aan Aadama yah ho…óoy aljanna aan e debbo maa √±aamee toon ko welata on kala …óo mbela-…óon taa …ìado-…óee kii lekki ndeen on jeyete e too√±…ìe."
  2,36,"Sey…óaane hoomti …ìe haa yaltini …ìe e mo∆¥∆¥ere nde …ìe ngonndoo Min mbi'i …ìe njippo-…óee ngonon a√±ondir…ìe ke…ìon √±ii…ìal dow lesdi ndii e dakmitaare haa happu yonta."
